<C>__{eliot}
<P>__{(amused)}
<D>__{mr. conran. we're at a wake. you should show more respect.}
<C>__{paul}
<D>__{i know she wasn't dead.}
<C>__{eliot}
<D>__{wasn't she?}
<A>__{eliot's suddenly tired of paul's allegations.}
<C>__{eliot}
